  "Description": {
    "English": "A living, fertile egg, <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">ready to hatch!</span><br><br>The weight inside this egg shifts constantly, as though the creature within is bouncing energetically.<br><br>Scans indicate the being within has the genetic potential to be a <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">sweet tempered</span> companion, soothed by gentle interactions.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一颗活生生的受精卵，<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">已可孵化！</span><br><br>这颗卵不停晃动，仿佛里面的生物正在兴奋地摇摆。<br><br>根据扫描结果显示，里面的生物拥有特殊的基因潜质，如果好好培养，日后将成为可通过温柔地安抚来进行互动的<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">温婉</span>同伴。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "有生命、可孵化的蛋，<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">且即將孵化！</span>蛋內的重量不停變動，就像裡面的生物正在激烈地跳動一般。<br><br><br><br>掃描結果顯示，該生物可能擁有以下形容的大小及特徵：<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">脾氣好</span>的同伴，能透過溫和互動安撫。"
  },
